info.title: Websak+ Integration API
info.description: This endpoint contains all the actions that are available for third party integrations.

get.summary: Fetches a document given its id.
Fetches all metadata for attachments and files on a given document
Fetches notes on a given document
Fetches reciveres on a given document
Fetches complementary data on a document

post.summary: Updates values in classification data on a given case

get.summary: Gets case details given the id for the case
Fetches documents within a given case.
Fetches classification on a given case
Fetches classification data on a given case
Fetches notes on a given case.
Fetches complementary data on a given case

post.summary: Returns a new case given the template id and titles given in the fields tittel1,tittel2
Returns a new case given the template id and titles given in the fields tittel1,tittel2
Fetches cases which contains given classifications

get.summary: Checks that current user can read given schema reference
Checks that current user can write to the given schema reference
You can use this action to check that your client works and is authorized.

post.summary: Updates values in complementary in existing or new revisjon
